  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They had all the things they needed over there, all the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what they call them over there?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like I told you, my English sometime-- all the tools to melt those teeth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they knew what kind of gold it is, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And almost-- I don't remember exactly-- every two weeks, or every month, or every week-- I don't remember exactly-- somebody of the SS man with a motorcycle was coming to the crematoriums and getting 10 kilos of gold.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the time when he was coming, every month, I guess, 10 kilos of gold.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How they were doing it, the French guys, they was melting the gold and making four-- four pieces of each piece of 250 grams each, which four pieces of those make one kilo.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were making 40 pieces of this gold, which was 10 kilos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was every week or every month come in and get it, the Germans from there, from the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now, we had good food because we could find from the transports a lot of food, a lot of diamonds, a lot of gold, because everybody was hiding something.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like my mother gave me the five gold pieces.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even in the cookies they were hiding even in the cookies some gold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were finding because we knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the shoes, we could find it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We knew on the clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this way, we had something good to eat, salami, bread, which was our life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, go ahead.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
